{"_id":"7c6d93DNCDgbNocX","name":"Sidekick","permission":{"default":0,"ZhC8ATjW2zJWoMct":3},"type":"move","data":{"name":"","description":"<p>Sidekick</p>\n<p>When you Recruit hirelings, you can always find someone who&rsquo;s trained as both an Adept and Warrior.</p>\n<p>If you take them on as your sidekick, they start with 4 loyalty.</p>\n<p>When you die or retire, they take up your sword.</p>","choices":"","moveType":"advanced","rollFormula":"","moveResults":{"failure":{"value":""},"partial":{"value":""},"success":{"value":""}},"class":"The Spellblade","rollType":"","rollMod":0,"requiresLevel":6,"requiresMove":"","moveGroup":""},"flags":{},"img":"icons/svg/mystery-man.svg","effects":[]}
{"_id":"8yDZy3vse1rvmTc4","name":"Spell Pierce","permission":{"default":0,"ZhC8ATjW2zJWoMct":3},"type":"move","data":{"name":"","description":"<p>Spell Pierce</p>\n<p>When you attempt to counter an arcane spell that would otherwise affect you, pierce it with your blade and roll+INT.</p>\n<p>On a 10+ the effects of the spell are halved.</p>\n<p>On a 7-9, you bear the brunt of the spell, but its effects on your allies are halved.</p>","choices":"","moveType":"advanced","rollFormula":"","moveResults":{"failure":{"value":""},"partial":{"value":"<p>On a 7-9, you bear the brunt of the spell, but its effects on your allies are halved.</p>"},"success":{"value":"<p>On a 10+ the effects of the spell are halved.</p>"}},"class":"The Spellblade","rollType":"INT","rollMod":0,"requiresLevel":2,"requiresMove":"","moveGroup":""},"flags":{},"img":"icons/svg/mystery-man.svg","effects":[]}
