{"_id":"v3y5GOcSqf71txBf","name":"Combat Caster","permission":{"default":0,"ZhC8ATjW2zJWoMct":3},"type":"move","data":{"name":"","description":"<p>Combat Caster</p>\n<p>Requires: War Wizard</p>\n<p>When you bond with your sorcerous blade, you may instill a spell you know of 5th level or below into your sword.</p>\n<p>When you work your Sword Magic, you may spend 1 hold to cast the spell immediately, whereupon it is released from your blade, no roll required.</p>\n<p>Once it is cast this way, you must bond again to store a new spell.</p>\n<p>You can&rsquo;t store more than one spell this way at a time.</p>","choices":"","moveType":"advanced","rollFormula":"","moveResults":{"failure":{"value":""},"partial":{"value":""},"success":{"value":""}},"class":"The Spellblade","rollType":"","rollMod":0,"requiresLevel":6,"requiresMove":"War Wizard","moveGroup":""},"flags":{},"img":"icons/svg/mystery-man.svg","effects":[]}
{"_id":"vkZG1MrI4jf0kKCp","name":"Stormbringer","permission":{"default":0,"ZhC8ATjW2zJWoMct":3},"type":"move","data":{"name":"","description":"<p>Stormbringer</p>\n<p>When you work your Sword Magic, on a 12+ you shake the earth and rend the skies.</p>\n<p>You may immediately add something to or remove something from the environment.</p>","choices":"","moveType":"advanced","rollFormula":"","moveResults":{"failure":{"value":""},"partial":{"value":""},"success":{"value":""}},"class":"The Spellblade","rollType":"","rollMod":0,"requiresLevel":2,"requiresMove":"","moveGroup":""},"flags":{},"img":"icons/svg/mystery-man.svg","effects":[]}
{"_id":"wFXhxPXzXCsKIwwV","name":"Sorcerous Blade","permission":{"default":0,"ZhC8ATjW2zJWoMct":3},"type":"move","data":{"name":"","description":"<p>Sorcerous Blade</p>\n<p>When you spend uninterrupted time with a nonmagical sword, about an hour or so, you turn mere metal into a medium for your arcane art - a Sorcerous Blade.</p>\n<p>When you deal damage with your sorcerous blade, you deal +1 damage.</p>\n<p>When you concentrate for a moment, you can summon the blade to your hand.</p>\n<p>You deal -[[/r 1d6]] damage with any other weapon.</p>","choices":"","moveType":"starting","rollFormula":"","moveResults":{"failure":{"value":""},"partial":{"value":""},"success":{"value":""}},"class":"The Spellblade","rollType":"","rollMod":0,"requiresLevel":0,"requiresMove":"","moveGroup":""},"flags":{},"img":"icons/weapons/swords/sword-guard-serrated.webp","effects":[]}
{"_id":"zNY0nnurIJSdKnn3","name":"Arcane Legacy","permission":{"default":0,"ZhC8ATjW2zJWoMct":3},"type":"move","data":{"name":"","description":"<p>Arcane Legacy</p>\n<p>You are part of a tradition, one thread of a weave in the tapestry of the world.</p>\n<p>Choose the nature of your arcane legacy</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Prophetic : Tell the GM a line from the prophecy - they&rsquo;ll tell you another.</li>\n<li>Bestowed: Name your mentor and write a bond with them.</li>\n<li>Ancient: Add your legacy&rsquo;s ancestral home to the map.</li>\n<li>New: Name at least one person or institution who is interested in you.</li>\n</ul>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>Choose your legacy&rsquo;s organization</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Military: You can spend 1 Sword Magic hold to keep a few foes busy in melee.</li>\n<li>Scholarly: You can spend 1 Sword Magic hold to expose an enemy&rsquo;s weakness or vulnerability.</li>\n<li>Secretive: You can spend 1 Sword Magic hold to make someone or something invisible temporarily.</li>\n<li>Self-taught: You can spend 1 Sword Magic hold to prove yourself stronger, tougher, or more dangerous than expected.</li>\n</ul>","choices":"","moveType":"starting","rollFormula":"","moveResults":{"failure":{"value":""},"partial":{"value":""},"success":{"value":""}},"class":"The Spellblade","rollType":"","rollMod":0,"requiresLevel":0,"requiresMove":"","moveGroup":""},"flags":{},"img":"icons/svg/mystery-man.svg","effects":[]}
